data.description:
If you are looking a multi-family WITH TWO PARKING SPACES in Old Mill Basin, look no further!  This three-story two-family brick townhouse is located at the center of Marine Park, Bergen Beach and Flatlands with fantastic amenities in every direction. Historic and handsome, this Multifamily is located a truly residential neighborhood with an established history and suburban atmosphere. A huge upside of potential at your fingertips. For the price of a condo, you can own this three-story brick. Park your car in your very own driveway and bring your groceries right into the home with none of the hassles of street parking! Special detail include, plenty of storage, a massive backyard as well as Southern & Northern exposures. 
The upper duplex is a super bright 3 Bed/ 1.5 Bath with a separate dining. The kitchen features stainless-steel appliances including a Whirlpool French-door refrigerator, a Frigidaire gas range stove and built-in microwave. Off the kitchen you have a ½ bath and a laundry closet with Whirlpool washer and dryer. Accessible from the kitchen is a patio deck and a staircase to a massive backyard making dining al fresco a breeze. There is also a spacious front door porch providing a picturesque barrier from the street and a lovely private spot to lounge in at the end of a long day. 
Head upstairs to the second floor where three generous sized bedrooms await, plus a full bathroom with a deep soaking tub, updated last year. 
The garden apartment is perfect the perfect one bedroom/ one bath for potential rental income or use the home as a one family! The garden unit also has access to the yard and can be entered through the size entrance. 
Easy access to the B100, Q35, B41 and connect with B/Q trains at Kings highway and 2/5 at Flatbush Avenue/Brooklyn College. Get an entire house for the price of a condo! 
DELIVERED VACANT.
